The Big Brother season 6 “Shine Ya eye” season 7 reunion has been slated to begin on June 2nd 2022. Organisers of the show made the announcement via their official twitter handle. They tweeted: “They are baccccccccckkkkk!   Check, pray for your friends – Teni     Cubana Priets joins protesting students     Ex-BBN star Pere acquires new car   “Your #BBNaija ‘Shine Ya Eye’ Housemates are back for an explosive Reunion! “Starting June 2 and showing every weekday on #AMUrban and #AMFamily at 10pm and 10:30pm respectively.’